OL,6,FMore recently, she also comes to visit
OL,7,Fher brother-in-law's grave after he
OL,8,Fpassed away.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Kelly said:
OL,11,F"I was amazed...It's so disrespectful.
OL,12,FPeople are laid here to rest and you
OL,13,Fdon't want to see that when you come
OL,14,Fin to see a loved one. It's a
OL,15,Fbeautiful cemetery and then you've got
OL,16,Fto look over at something like that. "
