OL,3,CGrieving families 'disgusted' at
OL,4,Cgraveyard fly tippers
OL,6,F"I'm just hoping that maybe if someone
OL,7,Fhas paid someone to dispose of this
OL,8,Frubbish because it would be
OL,9,Frecognisable. I think maybe just they
OL,10,Fdidn't realise that they didn't have a
OL,11,Flicence to dispose of this rubbish and
OL,12,Fmaybe they could get in touch with the
OL,13,Fcouncil."
OL,15,FKelly said her frustration is
OL,16,Fcompounded due to the fact that there
OL,17,Fis a rubbish tip five minutes down the
OL,18,Froad from the city council cemetery.
