OL,6,F"It's very disheartening to know that
OL,7,Fthis is a beautiful cemetery, and to
OL,8,Fsee someone do that, it's just not
OL,9,Fnice."
OL,11,FIn April 2025, the cemetery was also
OL,12,Ftargeted by criminals, who offloaded
OL,13,Frubble, tyres and litter close to some
OL,14,Fof the children's graves.
OL,16,FRelatives of those buried at the
OL,17,Fgraveyard want greater security
OL,18,Fmeasures in place, such as locking the
OL,19,Fgates at night or having cctv cameras
OL,20,Finstalled.
