OL,6,FThe first burial to take place at St
OL,7,FMary Extra Cemetery was in November
OL,8,F1879.
OL,10,FThe cemetery was taken over by
OL,11,FSouthampton City Council in 1922.
OL,13,FSouthampton City Council say they are
OL,14,Faware of the fly tipping incident and
OL,15,Ftheir teams are working hard to clear
OL,16,Fthe waste.
