OL,4,Cgraveyard fly tippers
OL,6,FIn a statement, Councillor John
OL,7,FSavage, Cabinet Member for Environment
OL,8,Fand Net Zero said: "Fly-tipping has a
OL,9,Fhuge impact on those that come to
OL,10,Fgrieve and I understand why people
OL,11,Ffeel so strongly about it. It is a
OL,12,Flazy and disgusting act.
OL,14,F"We've recently stepped up actions for
OL,15,Ftackling fly-tipping city-wide. I
OL,16,Funderstand people are asking for CCTV
OL,17,Fcameras to be installed, but due to
OL,18,Fthe sensitive nature and environment
OL,19,Fof the location, CCTV throughout the
OL,20,Fcemetery would not be appropriate as
OL,21,Fit would impose on those grieving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
